        <Bold FontSize="22">Orphans:</Bold>
        <LineBreak/>
        The complete hand only contains terminal tiles (1 or 9 ranked).
        <LineBreak/>
        e.g.:
        <LineBreak/>
        <InlineUIContainer>
            <StackPanel Orientation="Horizontal">
                <Image Margin="0,0,0,2" Source="1s.jpg"/>
