        <LineBreak/>
        <LineBreak/>
        <Bold FontSize="22">Nine Gates:</Bold>
        <LineBreak/>
        Any of the ranked tiles of the same suit forming 1112345678999 plus any tile of the same suit.
        <LineBreak/>
